" mapã¯ã‚­ãƒ¼è¨­å®š
" nnoremap ãŒ normal mode,
" inoremap ãŒ insert mode,
" cnoremap ãŒ command line mode
" Space w ã§ä¿å­˜ Space q ã§çµ‚äº†
